  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/0cef3e6d3cb5e15af54b0ef258f92026.avif?t=1760652344\" width=770 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's after midnight on the Quartzway Express, and everyone is woken up by signs of a MAGICAL ROBBERY! Players take on the role of Kabili as you tumble out of bed and work to solve your first ever mystery as a newly accredited arcane investigator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/8905947138a294047e869e69a03fc2a2.webp?t=1760652344\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/8905947138a294047e869e69a03fc2a2.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you'll meet your new investigative co-workers, question suspects, and search for evidence at the scene of the crime. Ultimately, you will defend the accused at a high stakes trial complete with cross-examination puzzles, surprise reveals, and lots of finger pointing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Can you solve the mystery and find the truth before it's too late?</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME PLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover clues by investigating with the power of point-and-click.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/b15da83c35c7d36f9b2a8fa1e2a87727.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/b15da83c35c7d36f9b2a8fa1e2a87727.webm?t=1760652344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/b15da83c35c7d36f9b2a8fa1e2a87727.mp4?t=1760652344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Meet and question suspects in addition to Kabili's larger than life investigative co-workers.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/c3a55b8e2562a81c754011c6c5fc5892.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/c3a55b8e2562a81c754011c6c5fc5892.webm?t=1760652344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/c3a55b8e2562a81c754011c6c5fc5892.mp4?t=1760652344\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Use collected evidence to solve \"Phoenix Wright\" inspired cross-examination puzzles at trial.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/f7ce2a4377ed1597019b090557205568.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/f7ce2a4377ed1597019b090557205568.webm?t=1760652344\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience a funny, cozy mystery as you get to the truth... <i>all before the train reaches its destination!</i></strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hand drawn characters and backgrounds.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fully sound designed with over 30 music tracks.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique comedic flare. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An hour long mystery filled with emotional twists and turns!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>The game is less than five dollars!</i></p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/0cef3e6d3cb5e15af54b0ef258f92026.avif?t=1760652344\" width=770 height=303 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's after midnight on the Quartzway Express, and everyone is woken up by signs of a MAGICAL ROBBERY! Players take on the role of Kabili as you tumble out of bed and work to solve your first ever mystery as a newly accredited arcane investigator. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/8905947138a294047e869e69a03fc2a2.webp?t=1760652344\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/8905947138a294047e869e69a03fc2a2.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" class=\"bb_img\" width=800 height=450 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Along the way, you'll meet your new investigative co-workers, question suspects, and search for evidence at the scene of the crime. Ultimately, you will defend the accused at a high stakes trial complete with cross-examination puzzles, surprise reveals, and lots of finger pointing. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Can you solve the mystery and find the truth before it's too late?</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAME PLAY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Discover clues by investigating with the power of point-and-click.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/b15da83c35c7d36f9b2a8fa1e2a87727.poster.avif?t=1760652344\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3581090/extras/b15da83c35c